{
  "script_id": "pick-theorem",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "在方格纸上画一个顶点都落在格点上的多边形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "不用刻度尺，只要数一数格点，就能算出它的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.36,
      "size": 21744,
      "text": "这个神奇的结论，就是皮克定理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "points",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "points-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/points-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "先把格点分成两类：落在多边形内部的，叫内部点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "points",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "points-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/points-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "落在多边形边线上的，叫边界点，我们画成空心圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "points",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "points-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/points-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "内部点记作 I，边界点记作 B，只要老实数出来就好。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-1",
      "filename": "formula-form-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/formula-form-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "皮克定理说，面积 A 等于 I 加上 B 除以二，再减一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-2",
      "filename": "formula-form-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/formula-form-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "每个内部点贡献一份，每个边界点只贡献半份。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-3",
      "filename": "formula-form-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/formula-form-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "最后减去的那个一，来自多边形闭合时的修正。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "shoelace",
      "line_id": "sl-1",
      "filename": "shoelace-sl-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/shoelace-sl-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "要验证它，我们用坐标直接算面积的鞋带公式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "shoelace",
      "line_id": "sl-2",
      "filename": "shoelace-sl-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/shoelace-sl-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "把顶点坐标交叉相乘再相减，取一半的绝对值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "shoelace",
      "line_id": "sl-3",
      "filename": "shoelace-sl-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/shoelace-sl-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "你会发现，鞋带算出的面积和皮克公式分毫不差。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "切换不同的多边形，看内部点和边界点如何变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "无论形状多奇怪，两种算法给出的面积始终相等。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "数出内部点与边界点，代入 I 加 B 除二减一即可。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pick-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pick-theorem/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "简单一数就见几何之美，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
